summary:
So I didn’t think I’d care much about Whoopi Goldberg’s episode of David’s podcast...but I was wrong. 
Her talking about being...
body:
So I didn’t think I’d care much about Whoopi Goldberg’s episode of David’s podcast…but I was wrong.

Her talking about being nice, even when it’s hard, to Fans and people who come up…and talking about how she knew what it was like, gathering up all the courage…and knowing exactly what it feels like to try and say hi..i don’t know. It just really gave me hope, I guess? That there are celebrities like that.
